---
source: crates/biome_formatter_test/src/snapshot_builder.rs
info: scss/expression/interpolated-string-formatting.scss
---

# Input

```scss
a{content:"#{".5"}";}

a{content:"#{.5 + .6}";}

a{content:"#{foo(.5, .6)}";}

a{content:"#{".5" + ".6"}";}

a{content:"#{my-fn(  "foo"  ,  "bar"  )}";}

a{content:'#{my-fn("foo")}';}

a{content:'#{my-fn("\\.5")}';}

$media: "only screen and (min-width: #{map-get($grid-breakpoints, "sm")}) and (max-width: #{map-get($grid-breakpoints, "md") - 1})";

```


# Formatted

```scss
a {
	content: "#{"0.5"}";
}

a {
	content: "#{.5 + .6}";
}

a {
	content: "#{foo(.5, .6)}";
}

a {
	content: "#{"0.5" + "0.6"}";
}

a {
	content: "#{my-fn(  "foo"  ,  "bar"  )}";
}

a {
	content: '#{my-fn("foo")}';
}

a {
	content: '#{my-fn("\\.5")}';
}

$media: "only screen and (min-width: #{map-get($grid-breakpoints, "sm")}) and (max-width: #{map-get($grid-breakpoints, "md") - 1})";

```

# Lines exceeding max width of 80 characters
```
   29: $media: "only screen and (min-width: #{map-get($grid-breakpoints, "sm")}) and (max-width: #{map-get($grid-breakpoints, "md") - 1})";
```
